    ],
    "history": "The client has a history of substance abuse and has completed rehabilitation, indicating previous struggles with coping. He reports ongoing family difficulties, especially with his mother, characterized by feelings of rejection and emotional neglect. He has been obese since childhood and experienced bullying related to his weight, which likely contributed to a negative self-image and low self-esteem. These longstanding issues set the stage for current emotional and cognitive patterns.",
